      "role": "user",
      "content": "Okay, that's better. I appreciate the technical detail. One more thing though—I've heard that blockages in the tube can be a major safety issue. Besides actual ice buildup, what are some other things that can clog the pitot tube or the static port, and how do those blockages typically affect the airspeed readings in the cockpit?",
